Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:39.85,RMLyrics13,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}Me no mae ni aru subete ga Taisetsu na mono nanda ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:52.37,RMLyrics13,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}Ushinau koto kowagaru nante  Watashitachi mada nani mo iretenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:59.74,RMLyrics13,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}Aoi aoi kono hoshi ni Kagirinai mirai kasane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:05.00,RMLyrics13,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}(you) can make me free Kono mama kodou Kanjite itai
